*{{audio|en-us-surprise.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪz|-aɪz]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# Something not expected.
#: ''It was a surprise to find out I owed twice as much as I thought I did.''
#(''[[attributively]]'') Unexpected.
#: ''The surprise attack was devastating.''
# The feeling that something unexpected has happened.
#: ''Imagine my surprise on learning I owed twice as much as I thought I did.''

====Synonyms====
*(''something not expected''):
*(''attributively: unexpected''): [[unexpected]]
*(''feeling that something unexpected has happened''): [[astonishment]]

